  "label": "The Lantern Lockroom",
  "description": "The Lantern Lockroom forms a narrow, blast-lined storeroom set behind plasteel bulkheads within The Pallid Lantern’s reinforced gallery. Riveted shelving and cage-front racks rise to the low ferrocrete ribs, holding standardized crates, keg-strops, and sealed canisters arranged for rapid inventory under siege protocol. Hooded lumen strips cast a cold, even light over stenciled tally marks and hazard sigils painted directly onto the walls. Vent grilles and exposed auspex cabling continue through the ceiling spine, maintaining the enclave’s regulated air discipline and constant readiness.",
